  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine whether a combined behavioral and pharmacological
      intervention provided by a multidisciplinary team will further reduce LDL-C, smoking, BP and
      Hb-A1C in diabetic patients with A1c between 7% and 9% when compared to usual care.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
